					<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><span class="name"><a name="7836"></a><b>Xirothi</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Journeyman Scout<br /><br /><br />Joined: 07 Oct 2004<br />Posts: 164<br />Server: Lucan DLere</span><br /></td>
					<td class="row1" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
						<tr>
							<td width="100%">&nbsp;<a href="viewtopic.php?p=7836&amp;sid=12adbef1d672ec1d03b7d54d79346b8a#7836"><img src="templates/scouts/images/icon_minipost.gif" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a>&nbsp;<span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed Oct 13, 2004 2:03 pm<span class="genmed">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: continued...</span></td>
							<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="2" width="100%"><tr><td width="100%" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=7836&amp;sid=12adbef1d672ec1d03b7d54d79346b8a"><img src="templates/scouts/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td></tr></table></td>
